SPDX policy
-----------
Each source file SHOULD begin with an SPDX license identifier:
    SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later

If a file incorporates third-party code under a different license, keep that file’s
original license header and add the appropriate SPDX identifier for that license.
Do NOT remove third-party copyright notices.

Contributions
-------------
By submitting a contribution (code, docs, tests, etc.), you agree to license your
contribution under the same terms (AGPL-3.0-or-later). Please add your name (and,
optionally, affiliation) to the CONTRIBUTORS file or to the relevant commit metadata.

Third-party components
----------------------
If this repository includes vendored third-party components, their licenses and
copyright notices MUST be preserved in a NOTICE or LICENSE file in the same
directory as the third-party sources.

